These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 6

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-1::.
4 different pets are kept: bird, mouse, dog, pony
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, cycling, handball, volleyball
1. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is handball##5
2. the owner of the mouse is not the person who's sport is baseball##6
3. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
4. the owner of the dog is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
5. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
6. the person who's sport is baseball is not the owner of the dog##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |
| Beverage   | mouse   | pony    | bird    | dog |
| Sport      | volleyball | baseball | handball | cycling |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  manager, journalist, fisherman, dressmaker
There 4 different types of food: artichoke, grapefruit, lettuce, onion
1. the person eating artichoke is on the far right##1
2. the journalist is somewhere to the left of the fisherman##5
3. the person eating onion is somewhere to the left of the dressmaker##5
4. the journalist is not the person eating grapefruit##6
5. the person eating onion is on the left of the fisherman##1
6. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
7. the dressmaker is on the right of the manager##1
8. the fisherman is somewhere to the left of the manager##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |    3     |     4     |
| Beverage   | journalist  | fisherman    | manager | dressmaker    |
| Food       | onion | grapefruit | lettuce  | artichoke |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, sprite, water
House: modern, townhouse, art-deco, wooden
1. the person drinking water is not the modern house##6
2. the townhouse house is not the person drinking sprite##6
3. the art-deco house is on the left or right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##3
4. the townhouse house is the person drinking fanta##1
5. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the townhouse house##1
6. the person drinking fanta is in an odd position##4
7. the modern house is on the far left or far right##3
8. the art-deco house is somewhere to the left of the wooden house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |       2        |   3    |   4    |
| Beverage   | water       | hot-chocolate  | fanta  | sprite |
| Job        | art-deco | wooden | townhouse | modern  |

