.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-5::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, january, july, april
The people use 4 different means of transport: bike, boat, car, snowmobile
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the person driving the car##5
3. the person who's birthday is in april is somewhere to the left of the person driving the boat##5
4. the person who's birthday is in january is not the person driving the snowmobile##6
5. the person driving the bike is not the person who's birthday is in september##6
6. the person who's birthday is in july is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
7. the person driving the car is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |  2   |    3     |   4   |
| Beverage    | september        | april | july | january |
| Transport   | snowmobile | bike | boat     | car   |

