.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-6::.
House: palace, craftsman, tower, colonial
There are 4 different nationalities: australian, colombian, indian, polish
1. the australian is on the right of the palace house##1
2. the colonial house is not the colombian##6
3. the australian is on the far right##1
4. the colombian is somewhere to the right of the polish##5
5. the tower house is the tower house##1
6. the tower house is somewhere to the left of the australian##5
7. the tower house is somewhere to the left of the palace house##5
8. the craftsman house is somewhere to the left of the polish##5
9. the craftsman house is somewhere to the left of the polish##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |     3     |     4      |
| Movie-Genre   | craftsman | tower    | palace  | colonial   |
| Nationality   | indian  | polish | colombian | australian |

