.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-8::.
There 4 different types of food: pomegranate, grapefruit, mango, pepper
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, journalist, photographer, social-worker
1. the coach is on the left of the journalist##1
2. the social-worker is somewhere to the left of the photographer##5
3. the social-worker is on the right of the journalist##1
4. the journalist is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3
5. the person eating mango is on the left or right of the journalist##3
6. the coach is on the left or right of the person eating pomegranate##3
7. the person eating pepper is somewhere to the right of the person eating mango##5
8. the person eating grapefruit is not the social-worker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Beverage   | grapefruit  | pomegranate        | mango      | pepper          |
| Job        | coach | journalist | social-worker | photographer |

