.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-9::.
4 different games are played: chess, domino, bridge, scrabble
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, helicopter, skateboard, subway
1. the person playing chess is in an odd position##4
2. the person driving the helicopter is not the person playing scrabble##6
3. the person driving the airplane is somewhere to the right of the person playing bridge##5
4. the person driving the subway is in an even position##4
5. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
6. the person driving the subway is the person playing bridge##1
7. the person playing chess is not the person driving the subway##6
8. the person playing domino is somewhere to the right of the person playing scrabble##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |   2    |     3      |     4     |
| Job         | chess  | bridge | scrabble    | domino |
| Transport   | helicopter | subway | skateboard | airplane  |

