.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-10::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, funk, electronic, rock
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, surfing, swimming, weightlifting
1. the person who's sport is golf is not the fan reggae##6
2. the fan rock is on the left of the fan funk##1
3. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
4. the fan rock is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
5. the fan electronic is not the person who's sport is weightlifting##6
6. the person who's sport is surfing is not the fan funk##6
7. the person who's sport is weightlifting is in an even position##4
8. the fan electronic is the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |       2       |    3    |    4     |
| Pet     | electronic | reggae        | rock  | funk     |
| Sport   | golf     | weightlifting | surfing | swimming |

