.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-13::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, boat, ship, trike
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, romance, time-travel, western
1. the person driving the train is somewhere to the right of the person driving the boat##5
2. the person driving the boat is not the person watching romance movies##6
3. the person driving the train is the person watching western movies##1
4. the person driving the ship is somewhere to the right of the person watching romance movies##5
5. the person driving the train is between the person driving the boat and the person watching adventure movies##2
6. the person driving the boat is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Food          | trike | boat      | train | ship   |
| Movie-Genre   | romance     | time-travel | western   | adventure |

