2. the person watching mystery movies is the owner of the bird##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is between the owner of the goat and the owner of the bird##2
4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the owner of the snake##1
5. the person watching documentary movies is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |     3     |      4       |
| Beverage      | rat       | bird | snake     | goat     |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | mystery       | superhero | martial-arts |

