4. the person who's sport is baseball is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
5. the person who's sport is cricket is between the baccarat-smoker and the person who's sport is climbing##2
6. the baccarat-smoker is not the person who's sport is baseball##6
7. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Job     | bolivar  | chaman | davidoff | baccarat |
| Sport   | baseball | climbing | cricket   | water-polo |

