3. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
5. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the far right##1
6. the person drinking fanta is not the person who's sport is water-polo##6

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2      |     3      |     4      |
