.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-6-19::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, singing, skydiving, woodworking
There are 4 different favourite colors: white, turquise, emerald, red
1. the person who likes turquise is somewhere to the right of the person who likes emerald##5
2. the person who likes white is somewhere to the right of the person who likes turquise##5
3. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the person who likes white##1
4. the person who likes red is not the person who's hobby is board-games##6
5. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the person who's hobby is board-games and the person who's hobby is singing##2
6. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
8. the person who likes red is somewhere to the right of the person who likes turquise##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |     2     |      3      |      4      |
| Hobby   | singing | skydiving | board-games | woodworking |
| Pet     | emerald  | turquise      | white  | red       |

