2. the person drinking water is on the left or right of the fan salsa##3
3. the fan country is on the right of the fan folk##1
4. the fan country is not the person drinking almond-milk##6
5. the person drinking water is somewhere to the right of the fan salsa##5
6. the fan salsa is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1      |    2     |     3      |     4     |
| Beverage    | almond-milk | iced-tea | water      | mirinda   |
| Transport   | classical  | salsa   | folk | country |

 